### Enrichment
Steph Ango (Obsidian CEO) has published his vault organization approach emphasizing simplicity. Community discussion shows some finding numbered prefixes too rigid. The JD + PARA hybrid approach used here addresses this by using numbers for sort order only. Obsidian users on the forum debate folder-based vs tag-based organization — beestgraph does both, which is a strength.

